§ 2.</li><li>§ 3.</li></ul></li></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1994-07-11-785" id="dokument"><h1>Forskrift om utstyrskrav for pliktig periodisk kjøretøykontroll og om pris for slik kontroll hos biltilsynet.</h1><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1994-07-11-785/§1" data-name="§1" data-partID="§1" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/" id="paragraf-1"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 1</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1">Kontrollorgan som skal utføre pliktig periodisk kjøretøykontroll må ha følgende utstyr (avhengig av hvilke kjøretøytyper som kontrolleres):<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">løftebukk eller grav,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">retardasjonsmåler,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">lyskontrollapparat,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/4/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">pedaljekk,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/5/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Co-måler,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/6/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">manometre/mellomstykker for kjøretøy med trykkluftbremser,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/7/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-7"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/7/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">røykmåler for kontroll av dieseldrevne biler (fra 1. januar 1996),</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/8/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-8"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/punkt/8/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1-punkt-8-ledd-1">lambdaverdimålet for kontroll av personbiler (fra 1. januar 1998).</article></article></li></ul></article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1994-07-11-785/§2" data-name="§2" data-partID="§2" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/" id="paragraf-2"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 2</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1">For pliktig periodisk kjøretøykontroll utført hos biltilsynet betales følgende pris:<table><tbody><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Personbiler:</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">kr 250,-</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Tilhengere:</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">kr 300,-</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Biler forøvrig:</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">kr 450,-</td></tr></tbody></table></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2">I tillegg til prisen kommer merverdiavgift.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1994-07-11-785/§3" data-name="§3" data-partID="§3" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/3/" id="paragraf-3"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 3</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1">Forskriften trer i kraft straks.</article></article></main></body></html>